# FOCIUM

**Focium** is a next-generation AI-powered productivity app designed to help users focus, track performance, and enter a state of deep flow. With a reactive 3D liquid orb, immersive space-themed UI, and real-time AI voice assistant, Focium transforms focus into an interactive, evolving experience.

