---

## Overview
Focium merges neuroscience, AI, and immersive design into a single app that motivates users to achieve peak productivity. The core **Focium Orb** reacts to voice commands, session progress, and environmental input, giving a visual, fluid representation of focus levels.

---

## Features
- **3D Reactive Orb**: Liquid venom/slime-style orb that reacts to AI voice.
- **AI Voice Assistant**: Natural conversation, guidance, and motivation.
- **Focus Timer**: Deep Work, Pomodoro, and Custom Modes.
- **Immersive Space UI**: Neon glow, dynamic backgrounds, pulsing animations.
- **Analytics Dashboard**: Track sessions, streaks, and Focium Score.
- **Cross-Platform**: Android & iOS support.
- **Lifetime Purchase**: No subscriptions; premium features unlocked via one-time purchase.

---

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend**: Flutter (Android & iOS)
- **Animation**: Rive, Lottie (orb + micro-interactions)
- **Backend**: Firebase (Auth, Firestore, Analytics)
- **Audio**: AAC/OGG chimes, pre-recorded AI voice
- **Optional**: Unity/Unreal for real-time orb upgrades

